  "text": "In this appendix, we show that a combination of the supercurrents S α (z) andS α (z) is conserved on the open string worldsheet; in other words, the supercharges dz S α (z) + dzS α (z) annihilate the boundary state. This construction is subtle at the quantum mechanical level [CITATION_1] 23, [CITATION_2] . We shall prove it at the classical level by studying the boundary conditions on the worldsheet fields.",
